{"id":204,"ayahs":[{"number":107,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ ٱتَّخَذُوا۟ مَسْجِدًۭا ضِرَارًۭا وَكُفْرًۭا وَتَفْرِيقًۢا بَيْنَ ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ وَإِرْصَادًۭا لِّمَنْ حَارَبَ ٱللَّهَ وَرَسُولَهُۥ مِن قَبْلُ ۚ وَلَيَحْلِفُنَّ إِنْ أَرَدْنَآ إِلَّا ٱلْحُسْنَىٰ ۖ وَٱللَّهُ يَشْهَدُ إِنَّهُمْ لَكَٰذِبُونَ","translation":"AND [there are hypocrites] who have established a [separate] house of worship in order to create mischief, and to promote apostasy and disunity among the believers, and to provide an outpost for all who from the outset have been warring against God and His Apostle. And they will surely swear [to you, O believers], \"We had but the best of intentions!\" -the while God [Himself] bears witness that they are lying.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1342.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":73234,"position":1,"arabic":"وَٱلَّذِينَ","translation":"এবং যারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73235,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱتَّخَذُوا۟","translation":"নির্মাণ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73236,"position":3,"arabic":"مَسْجِدًۭا","translation":"মাসজিদকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73237,"position":4,"arabic":"ضِرَارًۭا","translation":"ক্ষতি করার","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73238,"position":5,"arabic":"وَكُفْرًۭا","translation":"ও সত্য প্রত্যাখ্যানের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73239,"position":6,"arabic":"وَتَفْرِيقًۢا","translation":"ও বিভেদ সৃষ্টির উদ্দেশ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73240,"position":7,"arabic":"بَيْنَ","translation":"মাঝে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73241,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":"মু'মিনদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73242,"position":9,"arabic":"وَإِرْصَادًۭا","translation":"ও ঘাঁটি হিসেবে (ব্যবহারের জন্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73243,"position":10,"arabic":"لِّمَنْ","translation":"জন্যে তার যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73244,"position":11,"arabic":"حَارَبَ","translation":"যুদ্ধ করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73245,"position":12,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73246,"position":13,"arabic":"وَرَسُولَهُۥ","translation":"ও তাঁর রাসূলের (বিরুদ্ধে)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73247,"position":14,"arabic":"مِن","translation":"থেকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73248,"position":15,"arabic":"قَبْلُ ۚ","translation":"পূর্ব","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73250,"position":16,"arabic":"وَلَيَحْلِفُنَّ","translation":"এবং অবশ্যই তারা শপথ করবেই","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73251,"position":17,"arabic":"إِنْ","translation":"\"না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73252,"position":18,"arabic":"أَرَدْنَآ","translation":"ইচ্ছে করেছিলাম আমরা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73253,"position":19,"arabic":"إِلَّا","translation":"এ ছাড়া","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73254,"position":20,"arabic":"ٱلْحُسْنَىٰ ۖ","translation":"উত্তম\"","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73256,"position":21,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_023.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73257,"position":22,"arabic":"يَشْهَدُ","translation":"সাক্ষ্য দিচ্ছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73258,"position":23,"arabic":"إِنَّهُمْ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই তারা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73259,"position":24,"arabic":"لَكَـٰذِبُونَ","translation":"অবশ্যই মিথ্যাবাদী","audioUrl":"wbw/009_107_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73260,"position":25,"arabic":"١٠٧","translation":"(১০৭)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":108,"arabic":"لَا تَقُمْ فِيهِ أَبَدًۭا ۚ لَّمَسْجِدٌ أُسِّسَ عَلَى ٱلتَّقْوَىٰ مِنْ أَوَّلِ يَوْمٍ أَحَقُّ أَن تَقُومَ فِيهِ ۚ فِيهِ رِجَالٌۭ يُحِبُّونَ أَن يَتَطَهَّرُوا۟ ۚ وَٱللَّهُ يُحِبُّ ٱلْمُطَّهِّرِينَ","translation":"Never set foot in such a place! Only a house of worship founded, from the very first day, upon God-consciousness is worthy of thy setting foot therein -[a house of worship] wherein there are men desirous of growing in purity: for God loves all who purify themselves.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1343.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":73555,"position":1,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73556,"position":2,"arabic":"تَقُمْ","translation":"তুমি দাঁড়াবে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73557,"position":3,"arabic":"فِيهِ","translation":"মধ্যে তার","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73558,"position":4,"arabic":"أَبَدًۭا ۚ","translation":"কখনও","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73560,"position":5,"arabic":"لَّمَسْجِدٌ","translation":"অবশ্যই যে মাসজিদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73561,"position":6,"arabic":"أُسِّسَ","translation":"ভিত্তি স্হাপিত হয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73562,"position":7,"arabic":"عَلَى","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73563,"position":8,"arabic":"ٱلتَّقْوَىٰ","translation":"তাকওয়ার","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73564,"position":9,"arabic":"مِنْ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73565,"position":10,"arabic":"أَوَّلِ","translation":"প্রথম","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73566,"position":11,"arabic":"يَوْمٍ","translation":"দিন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73567,"position":12,"arabic":"أَحَقُّ","translation":"অধিকযোগ্য","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73568,"position":13,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73569,"position":14,"arabic":"تَقُومَ","translation":"তুমি দাঁড়াবে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73570,"position":15,"arabic":"فِيهِ ۚ","translation":"মধ্যে তার (সালাতের জন্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73572,"position":16,"arabic":"فِيهِ","translation":"মধ্যে তার (আছে)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73573,"position":17,"arabic":"رِجَالٌۭ","translation":"(এমন) লোক","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73574,"position":18,"arabic":"يُحِبُّونَ","translation":"(যারা) পছন্দ করে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73575,"position":19,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73576,"position":20,"arabic":"يَتَطَهَّرُوا۟ ۚ","translation":"তারা ভালোভাবে পবিত্রতা অর্জন করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73578,"position":21,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73579,"position":22,"arabic":"يُحِبُّ","translation":"পছন্দ করেন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73580,"position":23,"arabic":"ٱلْمُطَّهِّرِينَ","translation":"পবিত্রতা অর্জনকারীদেরকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_108_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73581,"position":24,"arabic":"١٠٨","translation":"(১০৮)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":109,"arabic":"أَفَمَنْ أَسَّسَ بُنْيَٰنَهُۥ عَلَىٰ تَقْوَىٰ مِنَ ٱللَّهِ وَرِضْوَٰنٍ خَيْرٌ أَم مَّنْ أَسَّسَ بُنْيَٰنَهُۥ عَلَىٰ شَفَا جُرُفٍ هَارٍۢ فَٱنْهَارَ بِهِۦ فِى نَارِ جَهَنَّمَ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ لَا يَهْدِى ٱلْقَوْمَ ٱلظَّٰلِمِينَ","translation":"Which. then, is the better: he who has founded his building on God-consciousness and [a desire for] His goodly acceptance-or he who has founded his building on the edge of a water-worn, crumbling river-bank, so that it [is bound to] tumble down with him into the fire of hell? For, God does not grace with His guidance people who [deliberately] do wrong:","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1344.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":73751,"position":1,"arabic":"أَفَمَنْ","translation":"কি তবে যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73752,"position":2,"arabic":"أَسَّسَ","translation":"ভিত্তি স্হাপন করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73753,"position":3,"arabic":"بُنْيَـٰنَهُۥ","translation":"ঘরের তার","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73754,"position":4,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73755,"position":5,"arabic":"تَقْوَىٰ","translation":"তাকওয়ার","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73756,"position":6,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"এর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73757,"position":7,"arabic":"ٱللَّهِ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73758,"position":8,"arabic":"وَرِضْوَٰنٍ","translation":"ও তাঁর সন্তুষ্টির (জন্যে)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73759,"position":9,"arabic":"خَيْرٌ","translation":"উত্তম","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73760,"position":10,"arabic":"أَم","translation":"না কি","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73761,"position":11,"arabic":"مَّنْ","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73762,"position":12,"arabic":"أَسَّسَ","translation":"ভিত্তি স্হাপন করেছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73763,"position":13,"arabic":"بُنْيَـٰنَهُۥ","translation":"ঘরের তার","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_013.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73764,"position":14,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"উপর","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73765,"position":15,"arabic":"شَفَا","translation":"কিনারার","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73766,"position":16,"arabic":"جُرُفٍ","translation":"খাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73767,"position":17,"arabic":"هَارٍۢ","translation":"পড়ন্ত","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_017.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73768,"position":18,"arabic":"فَٱنْهَارَ","translation":"অতঃপর তা পড়লো","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_018.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73769,"position":19,"arabic":"بِهِۦ","translation":"সহ তাকে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_019.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73770,"position":20,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_020.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73771,"position":21,"arabic":"نَارِ","translation":"আগুনের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_021.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73772,"position":22,"arabic":"جَهَنَّمَ ۗ","translation":"জাহান্নামের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_022.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73774,"position":23,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"এবং আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_024.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73775,"position":24,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_025.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73776,"position":25,"arabic":"يَهْدِى","translation":"পথ দেখান","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_026.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73777,"position":26,"arabic":"ٱلْقَوْمَ","translation":"(এমন)সম্প্রদায়কে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_027.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73778,"position":27,"arabic":"ٱلظَّـٰلِمِينَ","translation":"(যারা)সীমালঙ্ঘনকারী","audioUrl":"wbw/009_109_028.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":73779,"position":28,"arabic":"١٠٩","translation":"(১০৯)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":110,"arabic":"لَا يَزَالُ بُنْيَٰنُهُمُ ٱلَّذِى بَنَوْا۟ رِيبَةًۭ فِى قُلُوبِهِمْ إِلَّآ أَن تَقَطَّعَ قُلُوبُهُمْ ۗ وَٱللَّهُ عَلِيمٌ حَكِيمٌ","translation":"the building which they have built will never cease to be a source of deep disquiet in their hearts until their hearts crumble to pieces. And God is all-knowing, wise.","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1345.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":74145,"position":1,"arabic":"لَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74146,"position":2,"arabic":"يَزَالُ","translation":"সর্বদা হয়ে থাকবে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74147,"position":3,"arabic":"بُنْيَـٰنُهُمُ","translation":"ঘর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74148,"position":4,"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى","translation":"যা","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74149,"position":5,"arabic":"بَنَوْا۟","translation":"তারা বানিয়েছে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74150,"position":6,"arabic":"رِيبَةًۭ","translation":"সন্দেহের কারণ (বীজ)","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74151,"position":7,"arabic":"فِى","translation":"মধ্যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74152,"position":8,"arabic":"قُلُوبِهِمْ","translation":"অন্তরের তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74153,"position":9,"arabic":"إِلَّآ","translation":"যে পর্যন্ত না","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74154,"position":10,"arabic":"أَن","translation":"যে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_010.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74155,"position":11,"arabic":"تَقَطَّعَ","translation":"ছিন্নভিন্ন হবে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_011.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74156,"position":12,"arabic":"قُلُوبُهُمْ ۗ","translation":"অন্তর তাদের","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_012.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74158,"position":13,"arabic":"وَٱللَّهُ","translation":"আর আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_014.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74159,"position":14,"arabic":"عَلِيمٌ","translation":"সবকিছু জানেন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_015.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74160,"position":15,"arabic":"حَكِيمٌ","translation":"মহাবিজ্ঞ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_110_016.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74161,"position":16,"arabic":"١١٠","translation":"(১১০)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":111,"arabic":"۞ إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ ٱشْتَرَىٰ مِنَ ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ أَنفُسَهُمْ وَأَمْوَٰلَهُم بِأَنَّ لَهُمُ ٱلْجَنَّةَ ۚ يُقَٰتِلُونَ فِى سَبِيلِ ٱللَّهِ فَيَقْتُلُونَ وَيُقْتَلُونَ ۖ وَعْدًا عَلَيْهِ حَقًّۭا فِى ٱلتَّوْرَىٰةِ وَٱلْإِنجِيلِ وَٱلْقُرْءَانِ ۚ وَمَنْ أَوْفَىٰ بِعَهْدِهِۦ مِنَ ٱللَّهِ ۚ فَٱسْتَبْشِرُوا۟ بِبَيْعِكُمُ ٱلَّذِى بَايَعْتُم بِهِۦ ۚ وَذَٰلِكَ هُوَ ٱلْفَوْزُ ٱلْعَظِيمُ","translation":"BEHOLD, God has bought of the believers their lives and their possessions, promising them paradise in return, [and so] they fight in God's cause, and slay, and are slain: a promise which in truth He has willed upon Himself in [the words of] the Torah, and the Gospel, and the Qur'an. And who could be more faithful to his covenant than God? Rejoice, then, in the bargain which you have made with Him: for this, this is the triumph supreme!","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/1346.mp3","surahId":9,"words":[{"id":74514,"position":1,"arabic":"۞ إِنَّ","translation":"নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/009_111_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74515,"position":2,"arabic":"ٱللَّهَ","translation":"আল্লাহ","audioUrl":"wbw/009_111_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74516,"position":3,"arabic":"ٱشْتَرَىٰ","translation":"কিনে নিয়েছেন","audioUrl":"wbw/009_111_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74517,"position":4,"arabic":"مِنَ","translation":"হতে","audioUrl":"wbw/009_111_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":74518,"position":5,"arabic":"ٱلْمُؤْمِنِينَ","translation":